    "is_free": false,
    "description": "《Battleboom》是一款战争题材的公平对战游戏，玩家将化身指挥官部署指挥编队，同时需要熟练掌握各单位的特性，找到自己喜欢并擅长的不同策略组合，竭尽所能消灭对方有生力量，并最终摧毁敌方基地，赢得胜利！来决战吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721720/extras/8a69454d605cefb6c9ef729646cacd38.avif?t=1634694605\" width=616 height=150 /></span><br><br><strong>1、即时战斗，临场决策</strong><br>游戏采用即时战斗模式，每一个单位摆放的位置、时机和每个单位面对的敌人、战场环境都将决定战斗的最终胜负，充分熟悉编队中的每一个单位，并根据对手选择不同的策略，是胜利的关键。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721720/extras/28c2f9bd46d5a0c1b33d6155614960e7.poster.avif?t=1634694605\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721720/extras/28c2f9bd46d5a0c1b33d6155614960e7.webm?t=1634694605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721720/extras/28c2f9bd46d5a0c1b33d6155614960e7.mp4?t=1634694605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>2、多种组合，千变万化</strong><br>人海流、机械流、建筑流、兵营流、控制流，你到底喜欢哪一款？一张卡牌的变动就能决定战场走向，针对性布局和选择往往能够事半功倍。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721720/extras/c9418f0a07b4ccd04fb4323a5387ee63.poster.avif?t=1634694605\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721720/extras/c9418f0a07b4ccd04fb4323a5387ee63.webm?t=1634694605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721720/extras/c9418f0a07b4ccd04fb4323a5387ee63.mp4?t=1634694605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>3、加入军团，合作变强</strong><br>加入军团吧！这里不仅有更多的奖励、更多的伙伴，还能分享卡组和交流战斗经验。同时，军团的小伙伴还可以跟你交换自己想要的单位，优化你的编队，合作会让你更加强大。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721720/extras/5748059e91b674f978449814aba5f298.poster.avif?t=1634694605\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721720/extras/5748059e91b674f978449814aba5f298.webm?t=1634694605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721720/extras/5748059e91b674f978449814aba5f298.mp4?t=1634694605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>4、多种模式，随你挑选</strong><br>游戏提供多种战斗模式，有紧张刺激的1V1竞技，讲究配合的2V2对战（国际版独有），还有好友间的切磋，更有挑战自我的遭遇战（多种玩法，如限时挑战、防守挑战等），总有一个你喜欢。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721720/extras/84e5fae52cfbf038962e9287647b940e.poster.avif?t=1634694605\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721720/extras/84e5fae52cfbf038962e9287647b940e.webm?t=1634694605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721720/extras/84e5fae52cfbf038962e9287647b940e.mp4?t=1634694605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u><strong>开发者的话</strong></u>：<br>《战地指挥官》最早是我们工作室做的一款手机游戏，在全球100多个国家和地区上线，获得了IOS和GooglPlay的多次推荐，也受到了很多玩家的支持和肯定。<br>因为某些特殊原因，《战地指挥官》在中国大陆地区与海外的版本不一致，应很多玩家要求，我们将海外版本进行了PC版的制作，并在Steam平台进行发布，即现在《Battleboom》。<br>目前，我们优化了画面（适配PC的画质）、操作（如鼠标操作，位置判定等）等，后期我们会根据大家的反馈，不断改进更新。希望大家能在游戏中交到朋友，并给我们提出意见和建议，我们一定会努力将游戏开发的更好！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721720/extras/810e8c6b3ea519b2cdc6e3e1719be1fe.avif?t=1634694605\" width=616 height=150 /></span>",
